OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly low cloud, mist and fog
OL,6,Fwill lift to give some bright spells.
OL,7,FHowever, further low cloud, with mist
OL,8,Fand fog patches will gradually spread
OL,9,Facross the country from the west,
OL,10,Faccompanied by patchy rain. Feeling
OL,11,Fquite warm and humid.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FIt looks cloudy this evening
OL,14,Fand overnight with mist and fog
OL,15,Fpatches. There will be some showery
OL,16,Frain, especially at first and again
OL,17,Flater in the south. Warm and humid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
